sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant System as GIF System
    participant Database as GIF Database

    User->>System: Search for GIF
    System->>Database: Query GIFs based on search term
    Database-->>System: Return GIF results
    System-->>User: Display GIF results

    User->>System: Select GIF to send
    System->>Database: Save selected GIF for sending
    Database-->>System: Confirm GIF saved
    System-->>User: GIF ready to send

    User->>System: Send GIF
    System->>Database: Log sent GIF
    Database-->>System: Confirm GIF sent
    System-->>User: Confirm GIF sent successfully